<BYLINE>
<P>
From Associated Press 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
NEW YORK 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
More than 4,000 New Yorkers packed a church Friday to say goodby to Chancellor 
Richard Green, who died this week after 14 months of running the nation's 
largest school system. 
</P>
<P>
