Angeles County Sheriff's Department will send extra deputies to the area's gang 
hot spots this weekend to prevent retaliation. 
</P>
<P>
Deputies will enforce a 10 p.m.-to-sunrise curfew in the south end of Norwalk 
and the northern part of Artesia, where two rival gangs, Varrio and Chivas, 
have fought over the last year. 
</P>
