<HEADLINE>
<P>
VERDICT IN NORTH'S IRAN-CONTRA TRIAL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The bottom line of the North trial is that you can go to jail for opposing 
communism in Central America. Our Democratic-controlled Congress has shredded 
the Monroe Doctrine. 
</P>
<P>
FREDERICK D. MULLEN 
