<HEADLINE>
<P>
REVIEWING A LEGEND 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Liska says O'Day's 1981 autobiography is "High Life, Hard Times." The correct 
title is "High Times, Hard Times" -- and to sensationalize O'Day's 
well-publicized battle with drugs is to do an incredible injustice to one of 
the true -- one of the only -- survivors of the swing era. 
</P>
<P>
MICHAEL BRANTON 
</P>
<P>
Hollywood 
</P>
</TEXT>
