<P>
Game Story 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA051389-0131 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 57352 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
May 13, 1989, Saturday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Sports; Part 3; Page 17; Column 1; Sports Desk 
