<P>
EMPLOYMENT; HIRING; WAGES AND SALARIES 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA051389-0137 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 57364 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
May 13, 1989, Saturday, Orange County Edition 
</P>
